OL,3,CTrump unveils designs for luxurious
OL,4,Cskyscraper presidential library
OL,6,FDonald Trump has posted a video on
OL,7,Fsocial media appearing to show digital
OL,8,Frenderings for a luxurious
OL,9,Fpresidential library - including a
OL,10,Flarge gold statue of himself.
OL,12,FSet to dramatic music, the video
OL,13,Funveils a piercing tower along the
OL,14,FMiami skyline emblazoned with the
OL,15,Fsignature "Trump" lettering seen on
OL,16,Fhis other towers.
OL,18,FIt includes shots of a presidential
OL,19,Fjet parked in the lobby alongside a
OL,20,Fgold escalator.
OL,26,@wD@KOUwD@QO]
