OL,3,CTrump unveils designs for luxurious
OL,4,Cskyscraper presidential library
OL,6,FThe video also shows a giant ballroom
OL,7,Flike the one he's planning for the
OL,8,FWhite House, rooftop gardens and a
OL,9,Freplica Oval Office.
OL,11,FA credit says the design comes from
OL,12,FBermello Ajamil, a Miami-based firm.
OL,14,FTrump posted the video with no
OL,15,Fexplanation beyond a link to a new
OL,16,Fwebsite for the library - the website
OL,17,Fsays, "coming soon," with a link to
OL,18,Fdonate money.
OL,26,@yD@GOUyD@TO]
