OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774980702
OL,3,CTrump unveils designs for luxurious
OL,4,Cskyscraper presidential library
OL,6,FTrump's son Eric previously said the
OL,7,Flibrary will be "one of the most
OL,8,Fbeautiful buildings ever built" and
OL,9,F"an icon on the Miami skyline".
OL,11,FThe digital plans for the building
OL,12,Fshow it dwarfing the nearby Freedom
OL,13,FTower, a significant symbol to Cuban
OL,14,Fimmigrants in Florida.
OL,16,FThe post came hours after Florida
OL,17,Fairport was cleared to be renamed
OL,18,Fafter Trump on Monday.
