OL,3,CTrump unveils designs for luxurious
OL,4,Cskyscraper presidential library
OL,6,FFlorida Governor, Ron DeSantis, signed
OL,7,Fa bill allowing Palm Beach
OL,8,FInternational Airport to be renamed
OL,9,Fthe President Donald J. Trump
OL,10,FInternational Airport.
OL,12,FThe change is set to take place in
OL,13,FJuly, formally rebranding the airport
OL,14,Fnear Trump's Mar-a-Lago estate.
OL,16,FThis is the latest in a string of
OL,17,FAmerican institutions to have Trump's
OL,18,Fname and likeness put to them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
