OL,3,CTrump unveils designs for luxurious
OL,4,Cskyscraper presidential library
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe US Institute of Peace, and the
OL,12,FKennedy Centre have both had his name
OL,13,Fadded.
OL,15,FThere are also plans for the US Navy
OL,16,Fto build new "Trump-class
OL,17,Fbattleships", and for the US Treasury
OL,18,FDepartment to put Trump's signature on
OL,19,Fall new US paper currency.
